John:<br><br>
I don't know if I am floating in the water or &quot;belly up&quot; in the water...or dead in the water.<br>
The word &quot;gook&quot; does not really refer to people... it is a frustrated killer's way to depersonalize those who he is forced to kill.  It is an ugly word that harms only the user.<br>
I remember, up near the Cambodian border, some small children clamoring up to me to get their ration of hard candy.  A little girl smiled at my Native American features, touched my smooth naked arm and said, &quot;You..same same as me.&quot;<br><br>
Mita Kola, Cante Tinza... Akicita Was'te
